description:
A .NET Standard library provides some useful algorithms.
--------------------
When to use Sunday Quick-Search

Sunday Quick-Search algorithm in this libary provides the extension for three Types(IEnumerable<T> where T : IEquatable<T>, String, Byte[]), and it may not fit all situations, becouse it's more expensive. The list below shows when to use Sunday Quick-Search.

 DO NOT Find a single element(as an array with length 1) in an element collection.
 AVOID Find a String A in a longer String B, if the lengths of A and B are not too long.
 DO Find a byte array in a longer byte array.
 DO Find a IEnumerable<T> in a longer IEnumerable<T>.
summary: A .NET Standard library provides some useful algorithms.
